itemLabel: Terence Hamilton-Temple-Blackwood, 2nd Marquess of Dufferin and Ava

wikipedia_page.main: Terence John Temple Hamilton-Temple-Blackwood, 2nd Marquess of Dufferin and Ava DL JP (16 March 1866 – 7 February 1918), styled Lord Terence Blackwood between 1888 and 1900 and Earl of Ava between 1900 and 1902, was a British diplomat.
